help.help:
**__Sweplox Utilities Help__**

SweploxUtilities ver. 1.0, written by Dextnt
https://github.com/asdpoafomkasd

**Commands list:**

> `.verify` - Used by staff to verify a new member into the server
__Usage:__  ``.verify``  ``@User``


> `.nitrocolor` - Used by members with the Nitro Booster role to claim or remove their color
__Usage:__  ``.nitrocolor / .nc`` ``remove`` OR ``set`` ``color in hex``


> `.help` - The command you're using right now
__Usage:__  ``.help`` 


> `.adminnitrocolor` - Used by admin to change and remove other members nitro colors 
__Usage:__  ``.adminnitrocolor / .nc`` ``remove`` ``@User``  OR  ``set`` ``@User`` ``color in hex``


> `.move` - Used to move one or multiple users to another voice channel 
__Usage:__  ``.move / .mv`` ``channel`` ``@User`` ``@User`` (Up to 5 users)


> `.movemyself` - Used to move yourself + one or multiple users to another voice channel 
__Usage:__  ``.movemyself / .mvm`` ``channel`` ``@User`` ``@User`` (Up to 5 users)
